<p style="text-align: justify;"><br />
<strong>The Executive MBA (EMBA) program in Business Administration</strong> is being launched for the professional retraining of entrepreneurs, corporate executives, government officials and specialists, project managers, and professionals involved in strategic decision-making.</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Executive MBA</strong> is a 1-year intensive program designed to enhance modern leadership skills, develop strategic thinking, and improve professional qualifications.</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>During the program, you will:</strong></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>Learn to develop and implement competitive business strategies;</em></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>Gain in-depth insights into financial and economic performance of organizations;</em></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>Improve your decision-making skills in management and investments;</em></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>Act effectively as a leader in times of change;</em></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>Acquire skills in strategic planning and change management.</em></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>

