<p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" src="https://shakarim.edu.kz/upload/editor/news/F13.JPG" style="height:333px; width:500px" /></p>

<p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" src="https://shakarim.edu.kz/upload/editor/news/F12-1.JPG" style="height:333px; width:500px" /></p>

